726752f-a.title: Queens: Grand Avenue - 67th Street
726752f-a.text:
Grand Avenue (No's. 46-59), south side, east of 67th
Street, showig John Young's salogn in the foreground.
The center building houses Dibbel's Bakery.
January 1924.
